OL,3,CLabour and Conservatives rule out
OL,4,Craising VAT after General Election
OL,6,FFinance chiefs for both the Tories and
OL,7,FLabour have ruled out raising value
OL,8,Fadded tax (VAT) if their party were to
OL,9,Fwin the on July 4.
OL,11,FChancellor Jeremy Hunt warned family
OL,12,Ffinances could be "hammered" if there
OL,13,Fwas to be a rise to taxes on products
OL,14,Fand services.
OL,16,FWriting in the Telegraph, Mr Hunt said
OL,17,Fthat a Conservative government would
OL,18,Fnot increase income tax, national
OL,19,Finsurance and VAT throughout the next
OL,20,FParliament.
