OL,6,FClaims that were rubbished by Labour
OL,7,FShadow Chancellor Rachel Reeves, who
OL,8,Fpointed to her parties' claims that
OL,9,Fthe Tories are staring down a #71
OL,10,Fbillion blackhole with no plans to
OL,11,Ffill it.
OL,13,FReeves, however, also denied that her
OL,14,Fparty had any plans to uprate tax,
OL,15,Fnational insurance or VAT.
OL,17,FIn light of his claims, Hunt urged
OL,18,FLabour leader Sir Keir Starmer to make
OL,19,Fa similar commitment "on camera".
