OL,6,FMr Hunt also wrote: "A VAT increase
OL,7,Fwill hammer families' finances and
OL,8,Fpush inflation back up, just when we
OL,9,Fhave got it down to normal."
OL,11,FUK inflation slowed to 2.3% in April,
OL,12,Fthe lowest level since July 2021 and
OL,13,Fnear the government's 2% target,
OL,14,Faccording to the latest figures.
OL,16,FThe Conservative Party's new poster
OL,17,Fbears a giant red piggy bank bearing
OL,18,Fthe words: "If you think Labour will
OL,19,Fwin, start saving..."
